   "source": [
    "## 1 · Mission Definition & Requirements\n",
    "```\n",
    "The mission for this research platform is straightforward:\n",
    "\n",
    "                        ┌──────────── CRUISE  20 m/s ────────────┐\n",
    "                       /                                           \\\n",
    "  VTOL↑  ─ HOVER  ──/                                             \\── HOVER ─  VTOL↓\n",
    "  (60 s)   (60 s)                  1680 s = 28 min                   (included)\n",
    "\n",
    "The 30-minute endurance budget is split between:\n",
    "- 120 s of hover (60 s takeoff + 60 s landing, with margin)\n",
    "- 1680 s of cruise at 20 m/s (28 minutes)\n",
    "\n",
    "A 20% energy reserve is applied on top to account for wind, non-ideal\n",
    "flight paths, and battery degradation.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Platform Requirements\n",
    "\n",
    "| ID | Requirement         | Value                  |\n",
    "|----|---------------------|------------------------|\n",
    "| R-1 | VTOL capable       | True VTOL, tail-down   |\n",
    "| R-2 | Endurance          | ≥ 30 min total         |\n",
    "| R-3 | Payload            | 0.5 kg (sensor+compute)|\n",
    "| R-4 | Cruise speed       | 20 m/s (~72 km/h)      |\n",
    "| R-5 | MTOM               | < 25 kg (open category)|\n",
    "| R-6 | Max dimension      | ≤ 3 m                  |\n",
    "| R-7 | Propulsion         | Electric only          |\n",
    "| R-8 | Autopilot          | Pixhawk-compatible     |"
   ]
  },
