   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3 · Forward Flight Analysis — Size Matching Diagram\n",
    "\n",
    "### Theory\n",
    "\n",
    "Every flight phase imposes a minimum thrust requirement on the propulsion system.\n",
    "Using the parabolic drag polar  CD = CD0 + k·CL²  where  k = 1/(π·AR·e),\n",
    "each phase can be written as a curve of required T/W as a function of W/S:\n",
    "\n",
    "Cruise (steady level flight, eq. 2-52):\n",
    "    T/W = q·CD0/(W/S)  +  k/q·(W/S)\n",
    "\n",
    "Climb (best-climb speed, eq. 2-51):\n",
    "    T/W = RoC/V_climb  +  q·CD0/(W/S)  +  k/q·(W/S)\n",
    "\n",
    "Service ceiling (eq. 2-53):\n",
    "    T/W = RoC_ceil/V_mp  +  4·√(k·CD0/3)\n",
    "\n",
    "Maximum speed (eq. 2-59):\n",
    "    T/W = ρ·Vmax²·CD0/(2·W/S)  +  2k·(W/S)/(ρ·Vmax²)\n",
    "\n",
    "Stall limit (eq. 2-55):\n",
    "    (W/S)_stall = ½·ρ·V_stall²·CL_max\n",
    "    This is a hard upper bound on wing loading — the vertical dashed line on the diagram.\n",
    "\n",
    "The design point is where the upper envelope of all curves reaches its minimum\n",
    "inside the feasible region.  This minimises propulsion system size and therefore battery mass."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ── Forward flight parameters — loaded from config/forward_flight_params.yaml\n",
    "ff_params = ForwardFlightParams.from_yaml(CONFIG_PATH / \"forward_flight_params.yaml\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# ── Compute size matching diagram\n",
    "smd = compute_size_matching_diagram(\n",
    "    aero           = aero,\n",
    "    mission        = mission,\n",
    "    ff             = ff_params,\n",
    "    env            = env,\n",
    "    eta_propulsive = prop.eta_total,\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Size Matching Diagram — key outputs:\")\n",
    "print(f\"  Stall limit   (W/S)_stall = {smd.WS_stall:.1f} N/m²\")\n",
    "print(f\"  Design point  (W/S)*      = {smd.WS_design:.1f} N/m²\")\n",
    "print(f\"  Required      (T/W)*      = {smd.TW_design:.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"  Required      (P/W)*      = {smd.P_W_design:.4f} W/N\")"
   ]
  },
  {
